				 As far as I know, your pet CANNOT just go off on its' own and hunt. Why would you want to do that anyway? Pet -mage = dead pet. There are SEVERAL NPCs and Mobs that reguard your pet as hostile, and without the mage to cast 'renew elements' your pet will surely die and the Mob WILL come for you next. Remember mages, I have seen this posted elsewere before: TANK FOR YOUR PETS sometimes, especially when low on manna and pet is low on HP. I have killed many a yellow /con becuase after I shocked and renewed all I could I walked in, hit with my staff and took some heat off my pet. Happy hunting!<BR>
