				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				To get your pet to hunt, left click socials then pick a social to eliminate and right click it, you will then see a box with a flashing cursor after the name of the social you chose to eliminate. Hit backspace to eliminate that word and type p atck &lt;-(my suggestion) then tab and cursor will be in lower window.Type the following /pet attack. then click on button to set that as a social command. At this point you can make this a hot key. (left click and hold on command til it pops up as a key and insert it in hot key spot of your choice). now all you have to do is target an enemy and tap your hot key marked p atck and he or she is on thier way. If you dont want the hot key (even though its soooooo convenient), then just hit a target and then type /pet attack<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
hope i didnt over explain it to someone who already knows.....lol<BR>
<BR>
good luck to all and happy hunting ; - P****<BR>
